== 建省倡議 ==
2011年二月北荷蘭省、烏特勒支省以及夫利佛蘭省開始有合併的呼聲<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://nos.nl/artikel/216649-drie-provincies-denken-over-fusie.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-19 |archive-date=2016-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161010045348/http://nos.nl/artikel/216649-drie-provincies-denken-over-fusie.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這個合併案被[[荷蘭內閣|荷蘭內閣]]大力推動，在此聯盟下的協議有議將新的省份命名為[[蘭斯台德|蘭斯台德]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rtl.nl/(/actueel/rtlnieuws/)/components/actueel/rtlnieuws/2011/02_februari/04/binnenland/provincies-willen-fusie.xml |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-19 |archive-date=2012-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120322145606/http://www.rtl.nl/(/actueel/rtlnieuws/)/components/actueel/rtlnieuws/2011/02_februari/04/binnenland/provincies-willen-fusie.xml |dead-url=no }}</ref>，南荷蘭省的蘭斯台德地區則希望在此重新劃分案中也加入這個新的省份<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nrc.nl/nieuws/2011/02/04/randstadprovincies-onderzoeken-fusie/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-02-19 |archive-date=2016-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160316142559/http://www.nrc.nl/nieuws/2011/02/04/randstadprovincies-onderzoeken-fusie |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這些支持省份重劃的民意也大多希望這些地區合併為一個省份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zuid-holland.nl/contentpagina.htm?id=74163 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-02-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110724173855/http://www.zuid-holland.nl/contentpagina.htm?id=74163 |archivedate=2011-07-24 }}</ref>，不論南荷蘭省蘭斯台德是否加入這個新的省份，無庸置疑的成為荷蘭人口規模最大的省份。
